### Quotes API Endpoints
### Base URL: https://localhost:7001/api/v1

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001

### ============================================
### Authentication (get token first)
### ============================================

### Login to get JWT token
# @name loginRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### Store the token
@authToken = Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.accessToken}}

### Variables (update after creating resources)
@clientId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002
@carrierId1 = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000003
@carrierId2 = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000004
@quoteId =
@quoteCarrierId1 =
@quoteCarrierId2 =

### ============================================
### Quote CRUD Operations
### ============================================

### Create a General Liability quote
# @name createQuote
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "clientId": "{{clientId}}",
  "lineOfBusiness": "GeneralLiability",
  "effectiveDate": "2025-07-01",
  "expirationDate": "2026-07-01",
  "notes": "Annual GL quote request"
}

### Get all quotes
GET {{baseUrl}}/quotes
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Get all quotes with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/quotes?status=Draft&lineOfBusiness=GeneralLiability&page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Get quote by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/quotes/{{quoteId}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Get quotes summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/quotes/summary
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Get quotes by client
GET {{baseUrl}}/clients/{{clientId}}/quotes
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================
### Carrier Management
### ============================================

### Add first carrier to quote
# @name addCarrier1
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/{{quoteId}}/carriers
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "carrierId": "{{carrierId1}}"
}

### Add second carrier to quote
# @name addCarrier2
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/{{quoteId}}/carriers
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "carrierId": "{{carrierId2}}"
}

### Remove a carrier from quote
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/quotes/{{quoteId}}/carriers/{{quoteCarrierId2}}
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### ============================================
### Quote Lifecycle
### ============================================

### Submit quote to carriers
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/{{quoteId}}/submit
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Record a quoted response from carrier 1
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/{{quoteId}}/carriers/{{quoteCarrierId1}}/respond
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "isQuoted": true,
  "premiumAmount": 12500.00,
  "premiumCurrency": "USD",
  "conditions": "Subject to loss control inspection",
  "carrierExpiresAt": "2025-08-01"
}

### Record a declined response from carrier 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/{{quoteId}}/carriers/{{quoteCarrierId2}}/respond
Authorization: {{authToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "isQuoted": false,
  "declinationReason": "Outside appetite for this class of business"
}

### Accept carrier 1's quote (creates a draft policy)
# @name acceptQuote
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/{{quoteId}}/carriers/{{quoteCarrierId1}}/accept
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### Cancel a quote
POST {{baseUrl}}/quotes/{{quoteId}}/cancel
Authorization: {{authToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
